query:
DELETE FROM landings
WHERE
    landing_id IN (
        SELECT
            l.landing_id
        FROM
            landings l
            LEFT JOIN UNNEST($1::TEXT[]) u (landing_id) ON l.landing_id = u.landing_id
        WHERE
            u.landing_id IS NULL
            AND l.data_year = $2::INT
    )
RETURNING
    fiskeridir_vessel_id,
    landing_timestamp AS "landing_timestamp!"
